00:23:59.000 --> 00:24:00.880
Dia ada di sini, Ajeet.

00:24:06.720 --> 00:24:08.000
Di sana?

00:24:09.800 --> 00:24:11.520
Kenapa Ketki tidur di sini tadi malam?

00:24:16.960 --> 00:24:18.000
Ajeet,

00:24:19.000 --> 00:24:21.600
apakah kamu bertengkar tadi malam?

00:24:21.720 --> 00:24:23.120
Itukah sebabnya
dia tidur di sofa?

00:24:23.360 --> 00:24:25.800
Sama sekali tidak.
Seandainya kita bertengkar tadi malam,

00:24:25.880 --> 00:24:28.400
Saya akan tidur di
sofa, bukan Ketki.

00:24:30.440 --> 00:24:33.080
Entah kenapa Ketki
tidur di sini tadi malam.

00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:36.800
Ketki...

00:24:37.400 --> 00:24:39.200
Apa yang telah terjadi?
- Ketki.

00:24:40.680 --> 00:24:42.040
ketki!  - Ketki!

00:24:42.520 --> 00:24:43.760
Apa yang terjadi padamu?

00:24:45.400 --> 00:24:46.560
Kenapa dia tidak bangun?

00:24:50.040 --> 00:24:51.280
Ketki, bangun.

00:24:53.480 --> 00:24:55.080
Dia sudah bangun.  - Dia bangun!

00:25:07.920 --> 00:25:09.080
