00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:38.480
Radha, tunggu sebentar.

00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:43.000
Ya.

00:26:44.560 --> 00:26:45.520
Hati-hati.

00:26:48.720 --> 00:26:51.400
Radha, aku ingin bicara denganmu.

00:26:51.560 --> 00:26:52.880
Tentu.  Katakan padaku, Ketki.

00:26:57.120 --> 00:27:00.720
Radha, saat aku
berjalan-jalan tadi malam,

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:03.880
